    h1 A platform for creators (and hopefully hiveworks artists)
    p Heya Hiveworks peeps. I'm <a href="https://github.com/jjcm">Jake</a>, and I'm making a site I think you may be interested in. Nonio is a subscription site where your subscription is split evenly between everything you upvote that month. Think of it like Patreon meets reddit.
    br
    p A quick demo might be easier to understand. Lets say your subscription is $10 a month to the site. I take $1 to run the site, <strong>the remaining $9 is your contribution pool</strong>.
    br
    p Go ahead and upvote some posts below (click a tag to upvote) to see how your contribution would be distributed:
    br
